    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i should talk to my doc but i honestly can't get an appointment for like two weeks and i can't afford the gaps in my schedule. like, if i've been consistent with the 5mg and feeling this good, isn't it pretty safe to just scale it back a bit? i just want to avoid being on heavy meds forever if i don't have to be. wouldn't a lower dose like 2mg be a reasonable way to transition?",
